tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ProductionData (
  Date DATE,
  PondID INT,
  FeedType VARCHAR,
  FeedAmount INT,
  WaterTemperature FLOAT,
  OxygenLevel FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE production_data (
  production_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  species VARCHAR(50),
  weight DECIMAL,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE feeding_strategies (
  strategy_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  species VARCHAR(50),
  feed_type VARCHAR(50),
  feeding_time TIME,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE feeding_logs (
   log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   operation_id INT REFERENCES aquaculture_operations(operation_id),
   species_id INT REFERENCES fish_species(species_id),
   recipe_id INT REFERENCES feed_recipe(recipe_id),
   feeding_time TIMESTAMP,
   amount_fed FLOAT
);
